Developer Terms of Use
des:
Love grilled cheese? Grilled Cheese Recipes is the skill for you! Sara Lee Artesano Bread serves up mouthwatering creations to satisfy your ooey gooey cravings. Receive a recipe card with ingredients and step-by-step instructions for every recipe. And get ready to wow your taste buds. To get started, say, Alexa, Open Grilled Cheese Recipes.

FEATURES
• Variety of unique grilled cheese recipes
• Options for vegetarians and meat lovers
• Easy-to-follow steps
• Corresponding recipe cards with photos, ingredients and directions sent to your Alexa companion app
